Start
/ Creates an identity, signs a Data with it, verifies. End-to-end signing surface.
/ The cross-actor wire never carries PrivateKey ([Sensitive] excluded from View.Out) —
/ covered by C# WireOutput_Identity_*. This goal is the in-process happy-path companion.
- archive identity 'leakProbe', force, on error ignore
- create identity leakProbe
- set %data% = { "payload": "leak-probe" }
- sign %data%
- verify %data%, write to %verifyResult%
- assert %verifyResult.Success% is true, "signing surface intact"
